-- Texas RAC D - Metroplex/North Texas
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'TX-D-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'CPR, defibrillation, epinephrine, amiodarone. Consider mechanical CPR for prolonged resuscitation. Post-arrest targeted temperature management.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Texas RAC D - Metroplex/North Texas' AND c.state = 'Texas' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'TX-D-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'Stroke scale assessment. Document onset time. Glucose check. Rapid transport to comprehensive stroke center. Pre-notification required.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Texas RAC D - Metroplex/North Texas' AND c.state = 'Texas' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'TX-D-300', 'Trauma', 'Trauma', 'Trauma assessment. Hemorrhage control with tourniquets. IV access. Rapid transport. TXA for significant bleeding.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Texas RAC D - Metroplex/North Texas' AND c.state = 'Texas' LIMIT 1;

-- Texas RAC J - Capital Area Austin
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'TX-J-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'High-quality CPR. Early defibrillation. ACLS medications. Consider ECMO for refractory arrest in appropriate patients.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Texas RAC J - Capital Area Austin' AND c.state = 'Texas' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'TX-J-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'FAST assessment. Last known well time. Blood glucose. Transport to stroke center within 60 minutes.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Texas RAC J - Capital Area Austin' AND c.state = 'Texas' LIMIT 1;

-- Texas RAC N - West Texas El Paso
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'TX-N-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'CPR, defibrillation, medications per ACLS. Consider termination criteria for prolonged arrest.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Texas RAC N - West Texas El Paso' AND c.state = 'Texas' LIMIT 1;
